FcUtf16ToUcs4(3)                                                                                                                                                                          FcUtf16ToUcs4(3)

NAME
       FcUtf16ToUcs4 - convert UTF-16 to UCS4

SYNOPSIS
       #include <fontconfig/fontconfig.h>

       int FcUtf16ToUcs4 (FcChar8 *src, FcEndian endian, FcChar32 *dst, int len);

DESCRIPTION
       Converts  the  next Unicode char from src into dst and returns the number of bytes containing the char. src must be at least len bytes long.  Bytes of src are combined into 16-bit units according
       to endian.

Fontconfig 2.14.2                                                                             27 January 2023                                                                             FcUtf16ToUcs4(3)
